Rcouch changes
==============

0.7.0 - 2013/05/05
------------------

- support Erlang R16B
- updated the acceptor loop to use ranch 0.8.2 [1] from ninenine
- improved packaging. now use node_package [2] from Basho
- fix view seq changes
- fix couch_httpd boot
- fix acceptor loop on Erlang R15

[1] https://github.com/refuge/ranch
[2] https://github.com/refuge/node_package
